snippet.title: AP Calculus AB FR Question: Continuity at a Point
snippet.description: This video takes a look at the Definition of Continuity at a Point. One typical AP Free Response Question that deals with continuity at a point is discussed.  A detailed answer is given that would be an acceptable answer on an AP Calculus AB exam.
